  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not far from where we lived, there was a big hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I remember tobogganing on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So those are the kind of memories that, that I have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They're not extensive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But, but they're good memories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They're memories of, of a good life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- my father was born in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had several sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't be surprised if there were as many as five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was the only brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His father died when he was young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, again, don't know what that means, because, you know, it could be when he was a boy, or it could be when he was a teenager or a young man.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know from speaking to the aunt that lived in Canada when I came to Canada, that they all strived for him to get an education.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in fact, he is the only one in the family that received a very good education.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they came from an Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think it was not that common in the time for someone to go to university and get that kind of education that he did from an Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was-- they called him [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe it's, it's Isaac or Izrack, something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they called him [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, on the other hand, was born in Brody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Brody at the time was under the Austrians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in fact, they considered themselves of the Deutsche Kultur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, like in most of Galicia, education and culture and all kinds of things that had to do with theater and music and all this-- it was a revival of the intelligentsia there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so my mother and my mother's brother went to school, obviously.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
